@page
@model MonopHelper.Pages.Version

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Version History";
}

<div class="card">
    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
        @ViewData["Title"]
    </div>
    <div class="card-body bg-light">
        <div class="divider mb-3">
            <h3>1.3 Builds</h3>
            <div class="h-line"></div>

            <h4>Version: 1.3.6</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Fixed authorisation on turn based game pages.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Fixed custom loan repayment amount and loan repayments on front-end.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Made dropdown panels in turn based games 100% view height.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Added all player's numbers to main screen regardless of who's turn it is.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h4>Version: 1.3.5</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Brand new turn based game
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        In turn based games, you can see who's turn it is and information relating to that player.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        All functionality of the standard game (legacy game) can be done in a turn based game.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Turn based games now track mortgaged properties and calculate the fee a player must pay when passing GO.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Turn based games now track reserved properties and calculate the option fee to pay in order to unlock the reserved properties.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Cards are now in a turn based game.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Players can be created and selected for games.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        The number of wins a player has is tracked.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="divider mb-3">
            <h3>1.2 Builds</h3>
            <div class="h-line"></div>

            <h4>Version: 1.2.5</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Card types now have a colour option.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h4>Version: 1.2.4</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Changed the jail penalty increase to 50% instead of Â£20.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Can only have a maximum of 3 unpaid loans at one time.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h4>Version: 1.2.3</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Major code base redesign. All core functionality has moved into a class library.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Changed how monopoly defaults are loaded into the game (default cards, chance, community chest, etc).
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Added the 'Monopoly Deck' which includes all the default cards.
                        The cards in this deck cannot be modified, but they can be copied into other decks.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Setup for full turned based game.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="divider mb-3">
            <h3>1.1 Builds</h3>
            <div class="h-line"></div>

            <h4>Version: 1.1.3</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Redesigned ASP.NET login page.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Tenant and User ID fixes.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Cards in a deck can now be moved or copied to a different deck.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h4>Version: 1.1.2</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Added version history.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Index page is a generic home page with links to areas of the website.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Added cards into the game.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Can manage cards by uploading/adding new cards, modifying existing ones, or removing cards.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Can create, edit, and remove different card types.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Different card decks based on difficulty.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Can select a card deck and play the cards in that deck.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h4>Version: 1.1.1</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Add users and tenants.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        All pages, except ASP.NET identity pages, require authentication.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Games are now based on users.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="divider">
            <h3>1.0 Builds</h3>
            <div class="h-line"></div>

            <h4>Version: 1.0.1</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Can track player triples.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Added version in footer.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h4>Version: 1.0.0</h4>
            <div class="list mb">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Added standard game.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Add players to games.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Track player numbers and jail cost.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Track properties handed in to free parking.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Track player loans and the amount that is due.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Can open games that are not deleted.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        Can remove games.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>